        "email taken",
        "duplicate",
        "captcha failed",
        "rate limit",
        "too many requests",
        "invalid email",
        "blocked",
        "sent you a code"
      ],
      "code_selector": "input[name='code'], input[inputmode='numeric'], input[type='text']",
      "code_submit_selector": "button[type='submit']",
      "notes": "Kling kirim KODE verifikasi (bukan link) ke inbox (dari klingai@kwai.com). Bot sekarang support code-based verify via _verify_email_code. Selector code_selector/code_submit_selector perlu diverifikasi lewat devtools."
    },
